data.title: The Voice for Real Estate in the San Fernando and Santa Clarita Valleys
data.meta_description: Explore the Southland Regional Association of REALTORS® (SRAR) homepage for valuable resources, expert insights, and networking opportunities tailored to Southern California's real estate professionals.
data.text:
The Board of Directors has approved a Bylaw amendment that now requires a vote of the general membership. As a REALTOR® member of SRAR, you have the right to vote on this proposed Bylaw amendment.

Electronic voting will conclude on Tuesday, August 27, 2024 @ 12:00 PM.

Read the proposed bylaw change here.

Access your ballot and vote electronically by logging into the Members Only Area HERE. You must be a REALTOR® member to vote. If you have any questions, or wish to obtain physical voting materials,

please contact Valerie Biletsky valerieb@srar.com.

Lace up your sneakers and join us for a fun-filled 5K at the Hansen Dam Recreation Area on September 7, 2024. Registration begins at 6 am to 7:45 am and the race starts at 8 am! Walk, run, or roll at your own pace. This event is open to everyone, regardless of age or ability. Bring your family, friends, or coworkers for a team-building adventure.
